        <message_html><![CDATA[<div style="caret-color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard; text-size-adjust: auto;">
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;Hi ${request_number.hiring_manager},<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>CANDIDATES <span style="text-decoration: underline;">CAN NOT</span> BEGIN WORKING UNTIL HUMAN RESOURCES PROVIDES THE HIRING MANAGER WITH FINAL CLEARANCE ALONG WITH THE ELIGIBLE START DATE IN WRITING VIA EMAIL.</strong></span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong>Note this is an automated communication being sent by Human Resources.&nbsp;</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">HIRING MANAGER ACTION NEEDED.</span></strong> We ask that you do not forward this email to candidates, this message is intended for the department hiring manager or designee(s) only.&nbsp; The Background Investigation for the following individual has been processed. Below are the results of the Background Investigation. If applicable, below is a link to the Hiring Packet that the referenced candidate will need to complete at least<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>5-7 days before their anticipated date of hire</strong>, please have the candidate report to Human Resources in person to return their completed and signed Hiring Packet. For cleared candidates, please also advise the candidate of the University&rsquo;s participation in the Federal e-Verify program which requires us to verify their employment status with Homeland Security, as well as the BOR Policy regarding Direct Deposit.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>For candidates who have not been cleared there is nothing further the hiring manager will need to do other than to inform the candidate that they have not been cleared for employment at Clayton State University.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong>Candidate</strong>: ${request_number.first_name_of_candidate} ${request_number.last_name_of_candidate}</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong>Candidate BI Results</strong>: ${bi_results}</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"> <strong>Documents/Action Needed</strong> : ${hiring_documents_needed}</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong>The manager of the candidate(s) will need to submit a PAF in order to commence the hiring process</strong>. Please see links below for the Personnel Action Form (PAF) and New Hire Packets. If an Offer Letter is applicable, please contact Human Resources. For Accounting and Budget information please contact Scott McElroy.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong>New Hire Packets</strong>:&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="color: #954f72;" href="http://www.clayton.edu/human-resources/Forms/New-Hire-Packets"><span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration-line: none;">http://www.clayton.edu/human-resources/Forms/New-Hire-Packets</span></a></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong>Personnel Action Form (PAF)</strong>:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="color: #954f72;" href="http://www.clayton.edu/Portals/24/docs/personnel-action-form-PAF.pdf"><span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration-line: none;">http://www.clayton.edu/Portals/24/docs/personnel-action-form-PAF.pdf</span></a></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">If we can assist you in any other way, please feel free to contact us.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Thank you,&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Human Resources</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">o: 678.466.4230 | f: 678.466.4239</span></p>
</div>]]></message_html>
